---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Services" 
  description="Traditional Japanese landscaping, Ueki (Japanese garden trees), Bonsai services, and complete garden design in the Pacific Northwest."
>
  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1617543006359-46c0e2a86210?w=1920&q=80');">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Our Services</h1>
      <p>Ueki, Bonsai, and Japanese Garden Design</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <p class="lead" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">We specialize in three interconnected arts that together create authentic Japanese garden experiences. Each service can stand alone or work as part of a comprehensive landscape transformation.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Ueki Services -->
  <section id="ueki" class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-header">
        <h2>Ueki 植木 - Traditional Japanese Garden Trees</h2>
        <p class="service-intro">Ueki is the centuries-old Japanese art of cultivating, shaping, and maintaining trees specifically for garden landscapes. Our Ueki services honor these traditional techniques while adapting to your unique environment.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="service-grid">
        <div class="service-item">
          <h3>Tree Selection & Consultation</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Expert guidance on species selection for your climate and aesthetic</li>
            <li>Placement strategy for visual harmony and proper growing conditions</li>
            <li>Consideration of mature size and seasonal changes</li>
            <li>Long-term care requirements assessment</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="service-item">
          <h3>Niwaki Pruning & Shaping</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Traditional Japanese pruning to reveal natural tree architecture</li>
            <li>Structural pruning for elegant, balanced forms</li>
            <li>Cloud pruning (Tamamono) for pines and junipers</li>
            <li>Candling and needle plucking for pine health</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="service-item">
          <h3>Installation & Transplanting</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Professional installation following proper practices</li>
            <li>Mature tree transplanting with specialized equipment</li>
            <li>Soil preparation and amendment</li>
            <li>Staking and initial care protocols</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="service-item">
          <h3>Seasonal Maintenance</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Ongoing pruning and shaping to maintain form</li>
            <li>Species-specific fertilization programs</li>
            <li>Pest and disease monitoring and treatment</li>
            <li>Winter protection for sensitive species</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="species-list">
        <h3>Common Ueki Species We Work With</h3>
        <div class="species-grid">
          <div class="species-item">
            <strong>Japanese Black Pine (Kuromatsu)</strong>
            <p>Symbol of longevity and resilience</p>
          </div>
          <div class="species-item">
            <strong>Japanese White Pine (Goyo-matsu)</strong>
            <p>Elegant, fine-needled variety</p>
          </div>
          <div class="species-item">
            <strong>Japanese Maple (Momiji)</strong>
            <p>Stunning fall color and delicate form</p>
          </div>
          <div class="species-item">
            <strong>Flowering Cherry (Sakura)</strong>
            <p>Spring blooms and graceful branching</p>
          </div>
          <div class="species-item">
            <strong>Japanese Cedar (Sugi)</strong>
            <p>Evergreen structure and texture</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bonsai Services -->
  <section id="bonsai" class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-header">
        <h2>Bonsai 盆栽 - The Art of Miniature Trees</h2>
        <p class="service-intro">Bonsai is more than small trees in pots - it's a living art form requiring patience, skill, and deep understanding of horticulture. Our Bonsai services range from beginner guidance to advanced styling.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="service-grid">
        <div class="service-item">
          <h3>Custom Bonsai Creation</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Selecting and styling nursery stock into Bonsai</li>
            <li>Collecting yamadori (wild material) when appropriate</li>
            <li>Multi-year development plans for pre-Bonsai</li>
            <li>Air-layering to create new Bonsai from existing trees</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="service-item">
          <h3>Styling & Refinement</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Traditional and contemporary styling techniques</li>
            <li>Wiring for branch placement and movement</li>
            <li>Jin and Shari (deadwood techniques)</li>
            <li>Refinement of established collections</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="service-item">
          <h3>Repotting & Root Work</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Proper timing and species-specific techniques</li>
            <li>Root pruning for health and proportion</li>
            <li>Pot selection and custom sourcing</li>
            <li>Custom soil blending for optimal drainage</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="service-item">
          <h3>Care & Maintenance</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Daily care for collections (watering, feeding)</li>
            <li>Seasonal pruning and pinching</li>
            <li>Pest and disease management</li>
            <li>Overwintering protection</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="service-item">
          <h3>Education & Training</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>One-on-one instruction in Bonsai basics</li>
            <li>Species-specific care workshops</li>
            <li>Technique demonstrations</li>
            <li>Ongoing mentorship programs</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="styles-list">
        <h3>Bonsai Styles We Specialize In</h3>
        <div class="styles-grid">
          <div><strong>Chokkan</strong> - Formal Upright</div>
          <div><strong>Moyogi</strong> - Informal Upright</div>
          <div><strong>Shakan</strong> - Slanting</div>
          <div><strong>Kengai</strong> - Cascade</div>
          <div><strong>Han-Kengai</strong> - Semi-Cascade</div>
          <div><strong>Bunjin</strong> - Literati</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Garden Design -->
  <section id="design" class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-header">
        <h2>Complete Japanese Garden Design</h2>
        <p class="service-intro">Beyond individual trees, we create holistic Japanese garden spaces that embody traditional principles while functioning beautifully in modern settings.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="process-timeline">
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-number">1</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Initial Consultation</h3>
            <p>Site visit, vision discussion, style exploration, preliminary recommendations</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-number">2</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Concept Development</h3>
            <p>Site analysis, conceptual designs, plant palette selection, budget refinement</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-number">3</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Detailed Design</h3>
            <p>Comprehensive plans, hardscape specifications, lighting design, maintenance calendar</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-number">4</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Installation</h3>
            <p>Professional implementation, quality materials, project management, final walkthrough</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-number">5</div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <h3>Ongoing Support</h3>
            <p>Seasonal maintenance, plant warranty, design adjustments, long-term relationship</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Maintenance Plans -->
  <section id="maintenance" class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center">Maintenance Plans</h2>
      <p class="text-center" style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto var(--spacing-lg);">Japanese gardens mature and deepen with proper care. Our tiered maintenance plans ensure your garden thrives for years to come.</p>
      
      <div class="maintenance-grid">
        <div class="maintenance-plan card">
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3>Essential Care</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>2-4 seasonal visits per year</li>
              <li>Basic pruning and shaping</li>
              <li>Fertilization and soil care</li>
              <li>Problem diagnosis and treatment</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="maintenance-plan card featured">
          <div class="card-content">
            <div class="plan-badge">Most Popular</div>
            <h3>Premium Care</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Monthly visits during growing season</li>
              <li>Detailed pruning and refinement</li>
              <li>Comprehensive plant health management</li>
              <li>Priority scheduling and emergency service</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="maintenance-plan card">
          <div class="card-content">
            <h3>Bonsai Collection Care</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Weekly or bi-weekly visits</li>
              <li>Full watering, feeding, daily care</li>
              <li>Seasonal styling and repotting</li>
              <li>Show preparation assistance</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2>Ready to Begin Your Project?</h2>
      <p>Schedule a consultation to discuss your specific needs and explore how we can help transform your space.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: var(--spacing-md);">Schedule Consultation</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    height: 50vh;
    min-height: 400px;
  }
  
  .lead {
    font-size: var(--font-size-quote);
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }
  
  .service-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--spacing-xl);
  }
  
  .service-intro {
    font-size: var(--font-size-quote);
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
  }
  
  .service-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }
  
  .service-item {
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--spacing-md);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }
  
  .service-item h3 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }
  
  .service-item ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  
  .service-item li {
    padding: var(--spacing-xs) 0;
    padding-left: var(--spacing-md);
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .service-item li::before {
    content: "→";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  
  .species-list,
  .styles-list {
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  }
  
  .species-grid,
  .styles-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
    margin-top: var(--spacing-md);
  }
  
  .species-item strong {
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  
  .species-item p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: var(--font-size-small);
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }
  
  .process-timeline {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .timeline-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .timeline-item::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 39px;
    top: 80px;
    bottom: -48px;
    width: 2px;
    background-color: var(--color-secondary);
  }
  
  .timeline-item:last-child::before {
    display: none;
  }
  
  .timeline-number {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, #1e3829 100%);
    color: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
  }
  
  .timeline-content {
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--spacing-md);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }
  
  .timeline-content h3 {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }
  
  .timeline-content p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }
  
  .maintenance-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--spacing-lg);
  }
  
  .maintenance-plan {
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .maintenance-plan.featured {
    transform: scale(1.05);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(43, 79, 58, 0.2);
  }
  
  .plan-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    right: var(--spacing-md);
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-white);
    padding: 6px 16px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  
  .maintenance-plan h3 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }
  
  .maintenance-plan ul {
    list-style: none;
  }
  
  .maintenance-plan li {
    padding: var(--spacing-sm) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-background);
  }
  
  .maintenance-plan li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  
  .cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, #1e3829 100%);
    color: var(--color-white);
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
  }
  
  .cta-section h2 {
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }
  
  .cta-section p {
    font-size: var(--font-size-quote);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .maintenance-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .maintenance-plan.featured {
      transform: none;
    }
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .service-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .timeline-item {
      grid-template-columns: 60px 1fr;
    }
    
    .timeline-number {
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    
    .timeline-item::before {
      left: 29px;
      top: 70px;
    }
  }
</style>

